Roadkills case study

Week 9

1 Read in data

roadkill <- read_delim(here::here("data", "RoadKills.txt"), "\t")

roadkill

2 Clean data

roadkill <- 
  roadkill %>% 
  select(TOT.N, starts_with("D"))
roadkill

4 Modelling

4.1 Full model

M1 <- glm(TOT.N ~ ., family = poisson, data = roadkill)

4.2 Remove Water course

M2 <- update(M1, .~. - D.WAT.COUR)
summary(M2)

## [1] 0
roadkill <- roadkill %>% 
  add_column(
    M2_res = residuals(M2, type = "pearson")
  )
roadkill
roadkill %>% 
  ggplot(aes(D.WAT.RES, M2_res)) + 
  geom_point() + 
  geom_smooth()
## `geom_smooth()` using method = 'loess' and formula 'y ~ x'

roadkill %>% 
  ggplot(aes(D.PARK, M2_res)) + 
  geom_point() + 
  geom_smooth()
## `geom_smooth()` using method = 'loess' and formula 'y ~ x'

M3 <- glm(TOT.N ~ D.WAT.RES + 
            D.PARK + I(D.PARK^2) + I(D.PARK^3), 
          data = roadkill, family = poisson())
summary(M3)
##

roadkill <- 
  roadkill %>% 
  add_column(
    M3_res = residuals(M3, type = "pearson")
  )
roadkill %>% 
  ggplot(aes(D.PARK, M3_res)) + 
  geom_point() + 
  geom_smooth()
## `geom_smooth()` using method = 'loess' and formula 'y ~ x'

5 Fitted model

new_data <- 
  tibble(
    D.PARK = 0:25000, 
    D.WAT.RES = mean(roadkill$D.WAT.RES)
  )
new_data <- 
  new_data %>% 
  add_column(
    fit = predict(M3, newdata = new_data, type = "response")
  )
new_data
roadkill %>% 
  ggplot(aes(D.PARK, TOT.N)) + 
  geom_point() + 
  geom_line(aes(y = fit), data = new_data)
